title: DDFP 422: Divisional Round Review & Super Bowl Predictions
itunes:title: DDFP 422: Divisional Round Review & Super Bowl Predictions
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank, Maurice Jones-Drew, and Ike Taylor to breakdown all the Divisional Round action. The guys make their Super Bowl matchup predictions, as well as what is next for the losing teams. Lastly, yet another installment of "Dear Ikey". Is Carson Palmer the weakest link in Arizona? Is Marshawn Lynch done at Seattle? Will Ike and MJD accept their new theme songs? Find out more on DDFP.
